                        <div id="page-title">
                            风
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        




<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc0"><span>微风拂过你的脸颊，留下了一封泛黄的信纸</span></h2>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶————————————————————————————————————————————————————◀</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶————————————————————————————————————————————————————◀</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br />
<em>吾即是风</em><br />
<em>挥浓墨于笑谈中</em></p>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc1"><span>微风，安于内乱-原创主要文档合集</span></h2>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc2"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1135">SCP-CN-1135 呆滞转座子</a></span></h3>
<p><em>又回到那个孤单压抑的房间，不明无亮。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc3"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1273">SCP-CN-1273 欲倒载干戈，而你可安好？</a></span></h3>
<p><em>这生日，我下去给你过。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc4"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1278">SCP-CN-1278 轮</a></span></h3>
<p><em>Ты отправишься в рай（你将去往天堂）</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc5"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1323">SCP-CN-1323 粉红佳人</a></span></h3>
<p><em>我本就是天仙，何人有异议？</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc6"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1328">SCP-CN-1328 医者仁心</a></span></h3>
<p><em>救济苍生的地方为何要充满压迫与剥削&#8230;&#8230;</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc7"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1439">SCP-CN-1439 戏班</a></span></h3>
<p><em>人民战士被埋没在人们回忆的长河中。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc8"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1562">SCP-CN-1562 一生二，二生三</a></span></h3>
<p><em>涡虫风暴，血染长江。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc9"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1854">SCP-CN-1854 绝唱</a></span></h3>
<p><em>亿万年的底蕴，终敌不过贪婪的众生。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc10"><span>清风，徐徐落笔-原创故事合集</span></h2>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc11"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/storyofyou">下一次尝试</a></span></h3>
<p><em>愿每个创世神都能让他的造物发光。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc12"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/phone-call-reality">主控服务中心通话记录#17382</a></span></h3>
<p><em>对于Site-CN-429的一切，我们无能为力。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc13"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/dreamofyou">吾所深爱的梦</a></span></h3>
<p><em>我的怀中，空无一物，却满满当当。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc14"><span>诡风，刺骨寒心-原创Creepy Pasta合集</span></h2>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc15"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-tree">吾母老槐</a></span></h3>
<p><em>妈妈的职责已尽，是时候由孩子们来反哺了。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc16"><span>西风，融汇沟通-翻译主要文档合集</span></h2>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc17"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2163">SCP-2163 好莱坞</a></span></h3>
<p><em>那些五光十色只是骗局。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc18"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2764">SCP-2764 南极异兽</a></span></h3>
<p><em>我只希望这次不再是我了。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc19"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3681">SCP-3681 5 - 0</a></span></h3>
<p><em>那只球队？他们已经实现了他们的目标。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h3 id="toc20"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-5380">SCP-5380 吾的世界</a></span></h3>
<p><em>我让你来到了我的世界，随后……你就成为了我的世界。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc21"><span>喜风，笑口常开-翻译搞笑文档合集</span></h2>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc22"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-99826-j">SCP-99826-J 心灵螺丝</a></span></h3>
<p><em>（低声喃喃）我知道你在那里。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc23"><span>谐风，与君共勉-合著/参与/建议文档合集</span></h2>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc24"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1518">SCP-CN-1518 忆唐终曲</a></span></h3>
<p><em>作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6591621&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608733817" alt="Confucian Lee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6591621)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;">Confucian Lee</a></span></em><br />
<em>且听，这是来自大唐的末曲。</em><br />
<br /></p>
<h2 id="toc25"><span>狂风，啸纸喷墨-艺术作品合集</span></h2>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc26"><span><a target="_blank" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/happystormzhangart">至狂风呼啸处 风的艺作</a></span></h3>
<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>
<p>▶————————————————————————————————————————————————————◀<br /></p>
</div>
<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4761754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608733817" alt="H-Storm Z" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4761754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;">H-Storm Z</a></span>：请将你的一切倾诉写在信纸中，风会聆听。<br />
<br />
在恭喜风风喜提人事页的同时，我开始思考为什么自己到现在还没有人事页，难道是我不会写小短篇的原因？——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6331978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608733817" alt="carter lu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6331978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/carter-lu" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6331978); return false;">carter lu</a></span><br />
<br />
你鸽了一年来着吧&#8230;——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/artcgb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4847732); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4847732&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608733817" alt="ARtcgb" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4847732)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/artcgb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4847732); return false;">ARtcgb</a></span><br />
<br />
恭喜风风喜提人事！我的还遥遥无期……（哭）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6591621&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608733817" alt="Confucian Lee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6591621)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;">Confucian Lee</a></span><br />
<br />
▶————————————————————————————————————————————————————◀
